content: Hi Taylor, I saw Gamma Solutions is in Houston. Which big ideas keep getting pushed because no one has time?
what is working well with your current tools or website?
Oh, what should I tell you that?
I am just curious what parts of your business feel smooth versus what still feels messy.
Like, if you ever tell me about that, what are you going to do?
If you tell me what is working, I can suggest one small way to make the messy part easier. Sound okay?
Never touch your phone without watching it trust you.
I understand you are being careful. what is one small task that takes up too much of your time?
